  18. [@@@ocaml.warning "+a-4-30-40-41-42"]

  20. module S = Misc.Stdlib.String

  22. type is_global = Global | Local

  24. type constant =
  25.   | Const_closure of is_global * Clambda.ufunction list * Clambda.uconstant list
  26.   | Const_table of is_global * Cmm.data_item list

  28. type t = {
  29.   mutable constants : constant S.Map.t;
  30.   mutable data_items : Cmm.data_item list list;
  31.   structured_constants : (string,  Clambda.ustructured_constant) Hashtbl.t;
  32.   functions : Clambda.ufunction Queue.t;
  33. }

  35. let empty = {
  36.   constants = S.Map.empty;
  37.   data_items = [];
  38.   functions = Queue.create ();
  39.   structured_constants = Hashtbl.create 16;
  40. }

  42. let state = empty

  44. let add_constant sym cst =
  45.   state.constants <- S.Map.add sym cst state.constants

  47. let add_data_items items =
  48.   state.data_items <- items :: state.data_items

  50. let add_function func =
  51.   Queue.add func state.functions

  53. let get_and_clear_constants () =
  54.   let constants = state.constants in
  55.   state.constants <- S.Map.empty;
  56.   constants

  58. let get_and_clear_data_items () =
  59.   let data_items = List.concat (List.rev state.data_items) in
  60.   state.data_items <- [];
  61.   data_items

  63. let next_function () =
  64.   match Queue.take state.functions with
  65.   | exception Queue.Empty -> None
  66.   | func -> Some func

  68. let no_more_functions () =
  69.   Queue.is_empty state.functions

  71. let set_structured_constants l =
  72.   Hashtbl.clear state.structured_constants;
  73.   List.iter
  74.     (fun (c : Clambda.preallocated_constant) ->
  75.        Hashtbl.add state.structured_constants c.symbol c.definition
  76.     )
  77.     l

  79. let add_structured_constant sym cst =
  80.   Hashtbl.replace state.structured_constants sym cst

  82. let get_structured_constant s =
  83.   Hashtbl.find_opt state.structured_constants s

  85. let structured_constant_of_sym s =
  86.   match Compilenv.structured_constant_of_symbol s with
  87.   | None -> get_structured_constant s
  88.   | Some _ as r -> r
